        "content": "Each row is one trace. Click a Trace ID to open the waterfall and see a **single trace span multiple services and the Kafka boundary**.\n\n- **Card review** → `learning.review.completed send` (producer span) → click through to see `gateway-bff` HTTP → `svc-learning` → Kafka → `svc-progress` / `svc-notifications`.\n- **Conversation turn** → `speaking.turn` (WS root) → `svc-speech` + `svc-ai-dialog` → Kafka → `svc-vocabulary` → Kafka → `svc-learning`."
